--- partial column SELECT grant: must NOT leak column z ---
SHOW CREATE: ACCESS_DENIED
DESCRIBE:    ACCESS_DENIED
z via DESCRIBE name col present? no
--- partial SHOW COLUMNS grant: must NOT leak column z ---
SHOW CREATE: ACCESS_DENIED
DESCRIBE:    ACCESS_DENIED
--- all columns granted individually still does not imply table-level SHOW COLUMNS ---
SHOW CREATE: ACCESS_DENIED
DESCRIBE:    ACCESS_DENIED
--- full table SELECT grant: SHOW CREATE / DESCRIBE legitimately work ---
SHOW CREATE: CREATE TABLE
DESCRIBE columns:
x
y
z
